      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### \ud83c\udf3f Sustainability & Efficiency Hub\nThis comprehensive dashboard provides real-time visibility into the environmental and economic impact of the platform, tracking energy consumption, carbon footprint, and orchestration efficiency.\n\n**Key Metrics:**\n- **Efficiency:** Ratio of useful Pod power to total Node power.\n- **Carbon:** Based on an intensity of **150g CO2/kWh** (0.15 factor).\n- **Cost:** Based on an average electricity cost of **0.15 CAD/kWh**.\n- **Offset:** Yearly tree offset based on **21kg CO2 per tree/year**.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Header",
      "type": "text"
    },
